Kaduna State House of Assembly speaker  Aminu Abdullahi Shagali has resigned from his appointment. Shagali said his resignation was based on personal grounds in a letter dated February 25. “I, Aminu Abdullahi Shagali Speaker Kaduna State House of Assembly hereby resign my appointment as the Speaker Kaduna State House of Assembly on personal grounds,” he said in the letter. Former deputy speaker representing Igabi constituency Kaduna State, Yusuf Zailani, has been appointed as the new speaker of the assembly. To enable commenting and other interactive features, please switch to the more advanced .